<p>ã®é–¢ä¿‚ãŒã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨ã€(7.2.16)å¼ã¯</p>

\[\boldsymbol{\Gamma}^1 
= - \boldsymbol{A}^{-1} \boldsymbol{B}, \quad
\boldsymbol{\gamma}^1 
= \boldsymbol{A}^{-1} \boldsymbol{c} \tag{7.2.18}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚’è¡¨ã—ã¦ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
